		<div class="space-y-1">
			<p class="flex items-center">Working at <a href="https://engramapp.com" class="badge">
				<img src={EngramIcon.src} class="h-[25px] w-[25px] mr-1">
				Engram
			</a></p>
			<p class="flex items-center flex-wrap text-nowrap w-full">
				<span class="mr-1 mb-1">Creator of</span>
				<a href="/" class="badge">
					<img src={PomoIcon.src} class="h-[25px] w-[25px] p-1 rounded-lg mr-1">
					POMO Rings
				</a>
				<a href="https://evolvr.ink" class="badge">
					<img src={EvolvrIcon.src} class="h-[25px] w-[25px] p-1 rounded-lg bg-[#202020] mr-1">
					Evolvr
				</a>
				<a href="https://www.lunarhat.com" class="badge">
					<img src={LunarIcon.src} class="h-[25px] w-[25px] rounded-lg mr-1">
					LunarHat
				</a>
			</p>
		</div>
		<p>Rapid advancements in technology allow people to access the knowledge of the world at their finger-tips, but more and more knowledge is lost to the machine.</p>
		<p>Like with many things, I believe there can be a balance.</p>
